פרטים

Black Ops is an elite weight management system developed by the multi award winning R&D team at Grenade and has a unique stimulatory effect, designed to enhance mental and physical performance. Predominantly aimed at male users, Black Ops has a shorter duration of action than the original Grenade Thermo Detonator making it ideal for focused HIIT (High Intensity Interval Training) sessions and for training later in the afternoon or early evening. How it works When you try to solve a complex problem like getting rid of unsightly body fat, you can’t just come at it from just one angle. The body constantly adapts to changes in one or two metabolic pathways. So you have to consider all of the angles. That’s what the Grenade Research Team has done with Black Ops. The first thing you have to do when designing a world-beating fat loss support product is to strive to mobilize fat from fat cells. This is effected by caffeine – a must-have ingredient in any such product. Then, to ensure that the fat gets eliminated (and not just stored back in fat cells), you have to try and find some means to increase the metabolic rate and increase fat oxidation. This may be achieved by green tea … then Cayenne kicks in, in an attempt to assist green tea in ensuring maximum oxidation! Next, there are two other conditions, without which, you simply won’t burn maximum fat – you need to try to influence the right hormones and chemical messengers. This is where Blue green algae and Cocoa Extract come in. Blue green algae contains essential fatty acids and Phenylephrine. Essential fatty acids may be associated with decreased body fat mass and phenylephrine is involved with the body’s primary fat-burning hormone called norepinephrine. This may get the body’s primary signalling molecules – hormones – on your side. Finally, the icing on the cake is Cocoa Extract’s potential effect on nitric oxide. Most of us know nitric oxide as a vasodilator and pre-workout booster but studies suggest that it may be involved in fat metabolism also and in fact if it is blocked, the use of fat for energy virtually comes to a halt in the body. Not even satisfied with this five-pronged attack, Grenade Researchers have also added several micronutrients which have been evaluated to be substantially involved in the support of fat-loss metabolism and improvement of insulin function – crucial for properly handling dietary carbs! So while most fat-loss products are satisfied to influence one or two weight loss pathways in the body, Grenade Black Ops is designed to attack virtually all of them!
